prompt.title: Embedding for From Code to Conversation
prompt.content: The evolution of programming languages has progressed from physical hardware manipulation to low-level machine code, and then to high-level languages like Python and JavaScript. The book argues that the next revolution in this evolution is writing software in natural human language.
